  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">May 2021: The Government of Somalia declared a National Emergency due to the Drought situation and called for support in responding to the humanitarian crisis 3

FS situation still in process of deterioration.
Recent evolution of the Indian Ocean Dipole means outlook for less rain during October-December season across East Africa.
There&#xE2;&#x20AC;&#x2122;s an Acute Food Insecurity and Acute Malnutrition Analyses workshops in mid-august (seems it&#xE2;&#x20AC;&#x2122;ll be led by UN agencies) which will provide a more up to date analysis of the FS situation.</narrative>
  </description>
